# and lockfile (it runs `npm install` + `npm run build` itself). Everything below is
# either rebuilt on Vercel or irrelevant to the browser bundle. src-tauri/target alone
# is multi-GB of Rust artifacts and was blowing past Vercel's free upload file limit.
